This license grants NO rights whatsoever to the underlying game
"Slay the Spire 2" or to any of its code, assemblies, art assets, audio
data, fonts, scripts, configuration, or compiled resource packs.
"Slay the Spire 2" is © MegaCrit Inc. and is not affiliated with this
project.

To use this launcher you must own a legal copy of "Slay the Spire 2"
purchased through an authorised storefront. The launcher reads files
from a user-supplied copy at runtime; it does not contain, embed, or
distribute any MegaCrit material.

Redistribution of MegaCrit game files — including but not limited to
sts2.dll, sts2.deps.json, SlayTheSpire2.pck, any of the third-party
.NET dependencies the game ships in data_sts2_windows_x86_64/, FMOD
bank archives, Spine skeleton data, or any modified versions of the
above — is NOT authorised by this license and is likely to infringe
MegaCrit's copyright. Any such redistribution is the sole
responsibility of the redistributor.

Distributing builds of this launcher that include MegaCrit game files
in any form constitutes malicious or infringing distribution and is
explicitly prohibited.
